# --- Commit Type (Choose one) ---
# feat:     A new feature
# fix:      A bug fix
# docs:     Documentation only changes
# style:    Changes that do not affect the meaning of the code (white-space, formatting, etc)
# refactor: A code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
# test:     Adding missing tests or correcting existing tests
# build:    Changes that affect the build system or external dependencies (e.g., pom.xml, ci.yml)
# chore:    Other changes that don't modify src or test files

# --- Scope (Choose one for this project) ---
# project:  Project-level settings or configurations
# auth:     Core authentication logic (register, login, magic number)
# security: Spring Security configuration
# docker:   Dockerfile or containerization-related changes
# ci:       CI/CD workflow files (.github/workflows)
# readme:   Changes to README.md